subtasks.text: Store the dough in the freezer for 15 min.
Drop the dough in heaping spoonfuls onto a baking sheet.
Drag a fork across the top of each dough ball to add decorative striations.
Bake 15-20 min. The cookies will be lightly browned around the edges when done.
Let cool for 5 min and enjoy!
